Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT [db].[Title], [db].[Price] FROM dbo.DigitalBook db UNION ALL SELECT [dm].[Title], [dm].[Price] FROM dbo.DigitalMovie dm UNION ALL SELECT [da].[Title], [da].[Price] FROM dbo.DigitalMusicAlbum da UNION ALL SELECT [pb].[Title], [pb].[Price] FROM dbo.PhysicalBook pb UNION ALL SELECT [pm].[Title], [pm].[Price] FROM dbo.PhysicalMovieDVD pm UNION ALL SELECT [pa].[Title], [pa].[Price] FROM dbo.PhysicalMusicAlbumCD pa

Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT [e].[Id] AS EmployeeTableId, [e].[FirstName], [e].[LastName], [e].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Id] AS AddressTableId, [a].[EmployeeId] AS AddressTableEmployeeId, [a].[StreetAddress], [a].[City], [a].[State], [a].[ZipCode] FROM dbo.EmployeeShopper e LEFT JOIN dbo.EmployeeAddress a ON e.Id = a.EmployeeId

Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT [m].[Id] AS MemberTableId, [m].[FirstName], [m].[LastName], [m].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Id] AS AddressTableId, [a].[MemberId] AS AddressTableMemberId, [a].[StreetAddress], [a].[City], [a].[State], [a].[ZipCode] FROM dbo.MemberShopper m LEFT JOIN dbo.MemberAddress a ON m.Id = a.MemberId

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT [Title], [Price] FROM AllProductsBasicInfo WHERE Price > @MinPrice AND Price < @MaxPrice; END

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN INSERT INTO dbo.EmployeeShopper VALUES (@FirstName, @LastName, @PhoneNumber); END

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT [Id], [FirstName], [LastName], [PhoneNumber] FROM dbo.MemberShopper WHERE LastName = @LastName; END
